<i>Ona mora biti zatvorena.</i>

01:19:02.894 --> 01:19:04.331
Drži je sigurno.

01:19:04.366 --> 01:19:06.563
<i>To je Fiona Hajbridž.
Uhapsi je.</i>

01:19:07.103 --> 01:19:09.323
<i>Ne, ne, ne, ne, ne.</i>

01:19:19.049 --> 01:19:20.585
<i>Pazi.</i>

01:19:25.221 --> 01:19:26.992
Zaustavite sat.

01:19:29.327 --> 01:19:31.944
"Tragač duše", dušo!
